official_title: A bill to designate certain lands as wilderness.

summary.text: (Reported to House from the Committee on Interior and Insular Affairs with amendment, H. Rept. 94-1666) Designates approximately 346 acres of the Oregon Islands National Wildlife Refuge as the Oregon Islands Wilderness.

titles.title: A bill to designate certain lands as wilderness.
